People ex rel. McDonald, Appellant, v. Purroy et al., Respondents. Same v. McDermott, Respondent. Same v. Cahill, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 7, 1892.)

Argued before Bookstaver, Bischoff, and Pryor, JJ.

L. J. Grant, for appellant. W. L. Findly, for respondents.

No opinion. Writ of certiorari dismissed by consent.
